{"id":71665,"title":"Expanding use of palliative care in the oncology setting.","abstract":"The use of palliative care for patients with serious disease improves quality of life, reduces symptoms, and saves money. Unfortunately, too many patients endure needless suffering. Expanding awareness about palliative care among patients, providers, and policymakers will hopefully generate momentum for use of such services, thus benefitting patients with cancer and other advanced diseases. ","date":"2014-07-22","categories":"Neoplasms","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25046094","annotations":[{"name":"Disease","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Palliative care","weight":0.646624,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Palliative_care"},{"name":"Quality of life","weight":0.619721,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quality_of_life"},{"name":"Oncology","weight":0.60643,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oncology"},{"name":"Cancer","weight":0.54,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cancer"},{"name":"Suffering","weight":0.304527,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suffering"},{"name":"Symptom","weight":0.256114,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Symptom"},{"name":"Money","weight":0.0565064,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Money"},{"name":"Awareness","weight":0.0300804,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Awareness"},{"name":"Politician","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Politician"},{"name":"Momentum","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Momentum"}]}
